{
  "text": "Anexplained variable measurement scale was used according to past proposals Talpade 1994, Shoham and [CITATION_1] . The mother's perception may vary between 1 and 7 (where 1 = I had no influence, and 7 = I had all influence).",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "167949406"
